Keep going!

00:11:21.454 --> 00:11:24.290
Just a little bit further
till we reach the top!

00:11:24.324 --> 00:11:26.226
How much time do we have left?

00:11:26.259 --> 00:11:27.894
(Izzy grunting)

00:11:27.927 --> 00:11:31.297
(suspenseful music)

00:11:31.331 --> 00:11:32.732
