00:11:32.766 --> 00:11:33.733
Perfect.

00:11:33.767 --> 00:11:35.635
We could still make it!

00:11:35.668 --> 00:11:37.971
(Izzy grunting)

00:11:38.004 --> 00:11:41.608
Okay, Izzy, are you ready?

00:11:41.641 --> 00:11:42.742
(Izzy grunting)

00:11:42.776 --> 00:11:43.943
Let's do it!

