00:11:50.517 --> 00:11:51.751
Huh?

00:11:51.785 --> 00:11:53.753
(Izzy gasping)

00:11:53.787 --> 00:11:56.456
(air whooshing)

00:11:58.658 --> 00:11:59.959
(MetalGreymon groaning)

00:11:59.993 --> 00:12:01.327
(Garudamon groaning)

00:12:01.361 --> 00:12:02.462
(MegaKabuterimon groaning)

00:12:05.698 --> 00:12:08.301
(bright music)

00:12:09.369 --> 00:12:10.670
(T.K. screaming)

00:12:10.703 --> 00:12:12.839
(Kari, Sora, Izzy,
and Tai screaming)

00:12:12.872 --> 00:12:17.010
(MetalGreymon groaning)

00:12:17.043 --> 00:12:18.378
What just attacked us?

00:12:19.212 --> 00:12:20.180
Huh?

00:12:20.213 --> 00:12:21.347
He did.

00:12:21.381 --> 00:12:24.384
(suspenseful music)

00:12:28.822 --> 00:12:30.523
Okay, who's this?

